@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "User" as user

package "CatWorld (Spring Boot Monolith)" {
  [Spring Security] as sec
  [REST Controllers] as c
  [DTO + Mapper] as m
  [Services] as s
  [Domain (Entities + Rules)] as d
  [Repositories (JPA)] as r
}

database "MySQL (Docker)" as db

user --> sec
sec --> c
sec --> r : user lookup
c --> s
s --> m
s --> d
s --> r
r --> db

note right of s
Relevant business rules:
- endAt > startAt
- at least one cat per stay
- all cats in a stay share the same owner
- stay owner is consistent with the cats
- no overlapping stays per cat
end note

note left of sec
HTTP Basic is stateless.
Credentials are checked against
user_accounts.
end note

@enduml
